genresAdvancedInfo.name: swedish blues
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Swedish blues is a genre of music that blends traditional blues music with elements of Swedish folk music. The result is a unique sound that is both soulful and melancholic. Swedish blues artists often incorporate acoustic guitars, harmonicas, and other traditional instruments into their music. Some of the most popular Swedish blues artists include Anders Osborne, Louise Hoffsten, and Eric Bibb.
